\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"http://allendav.com/?p=233\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:548:\"This release marks a very significant milestone in the development of Seamless Donations for WordPress. Seamless Donations now supports Euros, Pound Sterling, Yen, and Canadian and Australian Dollars, in addition to US Dollars. All this and another new feature provided by the community &#8211; employer matching. International currency support has been a long time in [&#8230;]<img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=allendav.com&#038;blog=43405119&#038;post=233&#038;subd=allendav&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Allen S\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1843:\"<p>This release marks a very significant milestone in the development of Seamless Donations for WordPress.  Seamless Donations now supports Euros, Pound Sterling, Yen, and Canadian and Australian Dollars, in addition to US Dollars.  All this and another new feature provided by the community &#8211; employer matching.</p>\n<p>International currency support has been a long time in the making, and I am so very happy to launch this release.  At lot of the foundational work for currency support went into the most recent versions (which some of you noticed in the code), and all that work is live.</p>\n<p>I want to express my deeper thanks to all you who have encouraged and supported me thus far, and a special thank you to Jamie Summerlin for the work on employer matching and there is still much work to do.</p>\n<p>I would love especially to get some translations on board.  I will have French in the next release, and would love to add German, Italian, Spanish and other languages too!  Let me know here or on the support forums if you&#8217;d like to help with translations.  No coding skills required!</p>\n<p>As always, let me know if you have any questions, ideas, or run into any issues &#8211; the support forum is available <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/seamless-donations\" title=\"Seamless Donations Support Forum\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><em><a href=\"http://www.sxc.hu/photo/1379469\" target=\"_blank\">Photo by darrendean</a></em></p><br />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/allendav.wordpress.com/233/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/allendav.wordpress.com/233/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=allendav.com&#038;blog=43405119&#038;post=233&#038;subd=allendav&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:116:\"http://allendav.com/2014/01/21/seamless-donations-2-9-0-full-international-currency-support-and-matching-funds/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\