of a fundraising team. This team will be comprised of people who will oversee, coordinate and implement fundraising strategies, such as special events, campaigns by mail, online, and through local media such as television and news publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-22 17:41:41', '2014-08-22 17:41:41', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-5/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('74', '2', '2014-08-22 17:57:33', '2014-08-22 17:57:33', '<h3>We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.</h3>\r\nSupport the Hope Center\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</span></li>\r\n	<li><span>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</span></li>\r\n	<li><span>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"cmd\" value=\"_s-xclick\" />\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"hosted_button_id\" value=\"BEYXHT8VC9N3Y\" />\r\n<input type=\"image\" alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></form>Hayden Ministries has been privileged to have a steady and growing base of private financial supporters. These include local citizens who understand and appreciate the mission and ministry of The Hope Center, as well as local businesses and churches longing to see lasting and impactive change in t