\n<input type=\"image\" alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-72\" alt=\"Hope Center Logo \" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Hope-Center-Logo-Dimensions-e1408731975790.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"103\" /> <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></form>Hayden Ministries has been privileged to have a steady and growing base of private financial supporters. These include local citizens who understand and appreciate the mission and ministry of The Hope Center, as well as local businesses and churches longing to see lasting and impactive change in the Oroville Area. Once we moved into our new facility, our expenses almost tripled. Thankfully, as we have grown, our support base has grown. But there is still room for increase, as we are almost barely able to meet all of the necessary expenses.\r\n\r\nThis is why we will be establishing a comprehensive fundraising plan, which begins with the formation of a fundraising team. This team will be comprised of people who will oversee, coordinate and implement fundraising strategies, such as special events, campaigns by mail, online, and through local media such as television and news publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-22 18:27:30', '2014-08-22 18:27:30', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('114', '2', '2014-10-16 02:18:51', '2014-10-16 02:18:51', '<h3>We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consid