ws publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:18:51', '2014-10-16 02:18:51', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('115', '2', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '<span class=\"Apple-style-span\">[dgx-donate]</span>', 'Monthly Donation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'monthly-donation', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '', '0', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/?page_id=115', '0', 'page', '', '0'),('116', '2', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '<span class=\"Apple-style-span\">[dgx-donate]</span>', 'Monthly Donation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '115-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '2014-10-16 02:21:36', '', '115', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/115-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('117', '2', '2014-10-16 20:32:02', '2014-10-16 20:32:02', 'We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nSupport the Hope Center\n<ul>\n	<li>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</li>\n	<li>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</li>\n	<li>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</li>\n</ul>\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\">&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/monthly-button.jpg\" alt=\"Donate Monthly\" width=\"107\" height=\"48\" /></a>                        <input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\