Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:35:15', '2014-10-16 02:35:15', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('123', '2', '2014-10-16 02:35:51', '2014-10-16 02:35:51', '<h3>We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.</h3>\r\nSupport the Hope Center\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</li>\r\n	<li>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</li>\r\n	<li>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"cmd\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"_s-xclick\" /><a href=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/monthly-button.jpg\" alt=\"Donate Monthly\" width=\"107\" height=\"48\" /></a>                         <input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-72\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Hope-Center-Logo-Dimensions-e1408731975790.png\" alt=\"Hope Center Logo \" width=\"150\" height=\"103\" /> <img src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></form>Hayden Ministries has been privileged to have a steady and growing base of private financial supporters. These include local citizens who understand and appreciate the mission and ministry of The Hope Center, as well as local businesses and churches longing to see lasting and impactive change in the Oroville Area. Once we moved into our new facility, our expenses almost tripled. Thankfully, as we have grown, our support base has grown. But there is still room for increase, as we are almost barely able to meet all of the necessary expenses.\r\n\r\nThis is why we will be establishing a comprehensive fundraising plan, which begins with the formation of a fundraising team. This team will be comprised of people who will oversee, coordinate and implement fundraising strategies, such as special events, campaigns by mail, online, and through local media such as television and news publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:35:51', '2014-10-16 02:35:51', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('124', '2', '2014-10-16 02:39:46', '2014-10-16 02:39:46', 'We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.\r\n\r\nSupport the Hope Center\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</li>\r\n	<li>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</li>\r\n	<li>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\">&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/monthly-button.jpg\" alt=\"Donate Monthly\" width=\"107\" height=\"48\" /></a>                         <input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-72\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Hope-Center-Logo-Dimensions-e1408731975790.png\" alt=\"Hope Center Logo \" width=\"150\" height=\"103\" /> <img src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" />\r\n\r\n</form>Hayden Ministries has been privileged to have a steady and growing base of private financial supporters. These include local citizens who understand and appreciate the mission and ministry of The Hope Center, as well as local businesses and churches longing to see lasting and impactive change in the Oroville Area. Once we moved into our new facility, our expenses almost tripled. Thankfully, as we have grown, our support base has grown. But there is still room for increase, as we are almost barely able to meet all of the necessary expenses.\r\n\r\nThis is why we will be establishing a comprehensive fundraising plan, which begins with the formation of a fundraising team. This team will be comprised of people who will oversee, coordinate and implement fundraising strategies, such as special events, campaigns by mail, online, and through local media such as television and news publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:39:46', '2014-10-16 02:39:46', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('125', '2', '2014-10-16 02:41:08', '2014-10-16 02:41:08', 'We cannot continue our service without the financial support o\r\n\r\nf generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-72 size-full alignright\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Hope-Center-Logo-Dimensions-e1408731975790.png\" alt=\"Hope Center Logo \" width=\"150\" height=\"103\" />\r\n\r\nSupport the Hope Center\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</li>\r\n	<li>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</li>\r\n	<li>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\">&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/monthly-button.jpg\" alt=\"Donate Monthly\" width=\"107\" height=\"48\" /></a>                        <input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" />\r\n\r\n</form>Hayden Ministries has been privileged to have a steady and growing base of private financial supporters. These include local citizens who understand and appreciate the mission and ministry of The Hope Center, as well as local businesses and churches longing to see lasting and impactive change in the Oroville Area. Once we moved into our new facility, our expenses almost tripled. Thankfully, as we have grown, our support base has grown. But there is still room for increase, as we are almost barely able to meet all of the necessary expenses.\r\n\r\nThis is why we will be establishing a comprehensive fundraising plan, which begins with the formation of a fundraising team. This team will be comprised of people who will oversee, coordinate and implement fundraising strategies, such as special events, campaigns by mail, online, and through local media such as television and news publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:41:08', '2014-10-16 02:41:08', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('126', '2', '2014-10-16 02:44:37', '2014-10-16 02:44:37', 'We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 180px;\"></p>\r\nSupport the Hope Center\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</li>\r\n	<li>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</li>\r\n	<li>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\"><a href=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/monthly-button.jpg\" alt=\"Donate Monthly\" width=\"107\" height=\"48\" /></a>                        <input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" />\r\n\r\n</form>Hayden Ministries has been privileged to have a steady and growing base of private financial supporters. These include local citizens who understand and appreciate the mission and ministry of The Hope Center, as well as local businesses and churches longing to see lasting and impactive change in the Oroville Area. Once we moved into our new facility, our expenses almost tripled. Thankfully, as we have grown, our support base has grown. But there is still room for increase, as we are almost barely able to meet all of the necessary expenses.\r\n\r\nThis is why we will be establishing a comprehensive fundraising plan, which begins with the formation of a fundraising team. This team will be comprised of people who will oversee, coordinate and implement fundraising strategies, such as special events, campaigns by mail, online, and through local media such as television and news publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-72\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Hope-Center-Logo-Dimensions-e1408731975790.png\" alt=\"Hope Center Logo \" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:44:37', '2014-10-16 02:44:37', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('127', '2', '2014-10-16 02:45:12', '2014-10-16 02:45:12', 'We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSupport the Hope Center\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</li>\r\n	<li>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</li>\r\n	<li>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\">&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/monthly-button.jpg\" alt=\"Donate Monthly\" width=\"107\" height=\"48\" /></a>                        <input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n</form><img src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" />\r\n\r\nHayden Ministries has been privileged to have a steady and growing base of private financial supporters. These include local citizens who understand and appreciate the mission and ministry of The Hope Center, as well as local businesses and churches longing to see lasting and impactive change in the Oroville Area. Once we moved into our new facility, our expenses almost tripled. Thankfully, as we have grown, our support base has grown. But there is still room for increase, as we are almost barely able to meet all of the necessary expenses.\r\n\r\nThis is why we will be establishing a comprehensive fundraising plan, which begins with the formation of a fundraising team. This team will be comprised of people who will oversee, coordinate and implement fundraising strategies, such as special events, campaigns by mail, online, and through local media such as television and news publication. They will also search for grant opportunities and maintain current grant submissions and applications. This team will be intimately involved with all facets of Hayden Ministries in order to present a current picture of our status.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-72\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Hope-Center-Logo-Dimensions-e1408731975790.png\" alt=\"Hope Center Logo \" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />', 'Give', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 02:45:12', '2014-10-16 02:45:12', '', '11', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/11-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('128', '2', '2014-10-16 19:52:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'auto-draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2014-10-16 19:52:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '0', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/?p=128', '0', 'post', '', '0'),('129', '2', '2014-10-16 19:55:54', '2014-10-16 19:55:54', 'Where saints from different organizations gather to be the hands and feet of Jesus and reach-out to those who live in apartment complexes and other isolated conditions...we meet needs and minister to those who would not normally make it to the Center.  Come join us!  Meet in the HC Food Bank Parking Lot on Thursday\'s at 3:30pm...Blessings', 'City Quest', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'city-quest', '', '', '2014-10-16 19:55:54', '2014-10-16 19:55:54', '', '0', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/?post_type=services&#038;p=129', '0', 'services', '', '0'),('130', '2', '2014-10-16 20:04:17', '2014-10-16 20:04:17', '<h3 class=\"intro\">We are a non-profit Christian outreach that ministers to Butte County and the surrounding communities</h3>\r\nWe offer\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Emergency food and clothing</li>\r\n	<li>Resources to families who are battling many kinds of poverty</li>\r\n	<li>Food boxes distributed monthly</li>\r\n	<li>Commodities Distribution every fourth Wednesday of the month</li>\r\n	<li>Serenity Group (Faith Based Recovery Group)</li>\r\n	<li>Divine Appointment every Monday Night starting at 7pm (Worship, testimony, scripture and prayer)</li>\r\n	<li>Men\'s Ministry meeting every Thursday Night starting at 6:30pm</li>\r\n	<li>Home of the ACADC Counselors Institute (Association of Christian Alcohol and Drug Counselors), a licensed class that prepares individuals to sit for the State Exam and obtain their State of California Alcohol/Drug Counselors license.</li>\r\n	<li>Home of the Greater Oroville Homeless Coalition which provides housing solutions to those who are without shelter</li>\r\n	<li>In partnership with Starting Over Strong; expungement classes are offered bi-monthly</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Welcome to the Hope Center', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 20:04:17', '2014-10-16 20:04:17', '', '8', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/8-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('131', '2', '2014-10-16 20:09:19', '2014-10-16 20:09:19', 'Life Skills Academy is a collaboration that includes The Hope Center, the ACADC Institute,  local agencies, and churches to provide free basic life skills education in order to effect a positive change in peoples\' lives, helping them to contribute to the community, creating a better environment for individuals, businesses and law enforcement personnel, and even saving tax-payer dollars.', 'Life Skills Academy (LSA)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-16 20:09:19', '2014-10-16 20:09:19', '', '30', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/30-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),('132', '2', '2014-10-16 20:19:29', '2014-10-16 20:19:29', 'ACADC is nationally accredited by the National Commission for Certifying Agencies as required by the CA Department of Alcohol and Drug Programs.  The ACADC is authorized by the State Department of California Alcohol and Drug Programs to train, evaluate and issue the state certification of Professional Alcohol, Drug and Addictions Counselor.  It\'s curriculum has been reviewed and approved by the State of California Department of Alcohol and Drug Programs and meets the requirement to teach the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration\'s TAP 21 Addiction Counseling Competencies:  The Knowledge, Skills, and Attitudes of Professional Practice.\r\n\r\nThis Institute also provides Life Skills Classes, an Internship Program, counseling, and is a direct pipeline to local recovery programs in the City.', 'Association of Christian Alcohol & Drug Counselors Institute', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'association-of-christian-alcohol-drug-counselors-institute', '', '', '2014-10-16 20:28:49', '2014-10-16 20:28:49', '', '0', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/?post_type=services&#038;p=132', '0', 'services', '', '0'),('133', '2', '2014-10-16 20:24:32', '2014-10-16 20:24:32', 'The Greater Oroville Homeless Coalition is housed in the Hope Center.  The GOHC office is open on Tuesday\'s and Thursday\'s from 9:30am to 12:30pm.  They work to end homelessness one individual or family at a time, whether you are in trouble of losing your housing, or if you are trying to find housing.  If you need their assistance please call (530) 538-8399.  Feel free to leave a message; someone will call you back ASAP.', 'The Greater Oroville Homeless Coalition', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-greater-oroville-homeless-coalition', '', '', '2014-10-16 20:24:32', '2014-10-16 20:24:32', '', '0', 'http://orovillehopecenter.org/?post_type=services&#038;p=133', '0', 'services', '', '0'),('134', '2', '2014-10-16 20:32:07', '2014-10-16 20:32:07', 'We cannot continue our service without the financial support of generous donors. Consider a tax-deductible donation today.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSupport the Hope Center\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Deliver / mail a check or money order to the Hope Center</li>\r\n	<li>Donate belongings to Grandma\'s Mission of Hope Thrift Shoppe</li>\r\n	<li>Donate securely online via PayPal with any major credit card (no PayPal account required)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\">&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-118 size-full\" src=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/production/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/monthly-button.jpg\" alt=\"Donate Monthly\" width=\"107\" height=\"48\" /></a>                        <input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n</form><img src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" bor